version_description: Thank you for using MealMe! This app version includes bug fixes & optimizations.
Thank you for using MealMe! This app version includes a new interface to view a restaurant, along with bug fixes & optimizations.

We've pushed an incredible 14 updates over the past month to continue improving the product. Thanks for your continued support!

What's new:
- UI/UX improvements to the restaurant view
- Added new delivery services
- Several crash & bug fixes

As always, make sure to turn on auto updates to keep getting the best deals on food!
